{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was-- she was-- when I met her, she was already married to a wonderful young man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was exactly two years older-- two and a half years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, it was like-- it was like an explosion, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, she was so-- she is totally different than I was, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She is this-- she is so-- she knows exactly what it's at.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, she can-- she will enter a room, and she will assess the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She's got-- on one hand, she's got-- she has the kindness and gentleness and the most lovingest-- loving-- lovely person you could meet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other hand, she's very like my mother's, like my father's, like my paternal grandmother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She will enter a room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she will assess a situation, where she can, you know, the subtleties?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where she doesn't want to take advantage of the situation, but she will straightaway think how to turn it around into something positive that-- that can-- that it can make, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That she can-- something that you can not just feel, but that you can see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not to hurt anybody that you can see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she is the one that is this practical, you know this, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we just get on like a house on fire, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did you know her when you were growing up in Siemianowice?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, her mother was my dad's oldest sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she helped in bringing my dad up, because my-- my-- my paternal grandmother was very involved in the business in Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was the one with the-- with the touch, you know, that she really would create an environment, a very productive environment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, her mother, they lived in Radomsk, Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
